{"tid":687516,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"印度IT員工優秀？調查：95％程式碼測驗不合格","createTime":"2018-06-02T10:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T14:03:39.000Z","uid":1886,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c1bc2334a32018b09673066a2deb9097edeb919a","tid":687516,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"印度被喻為 IT 大國，由於不受種姓分級制度限制，當地很多年青人爭相入行，令全球各地都認為數學領域優秀的印度人可成為理想 IT 工程師。不過最近有研究表示，95％ IT 大學生的基礎程式編寫能力不合格，令人懷疑「IT大國」這個稱呼是否適用於印度。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/http-i.ftimg_.net-picture-3-000068003_piclink.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Fhttp-i.ftimg_.net-picture-3-000068003_piclink.jpg&h=a0c88eda&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n受可口可樂、亞馬遜等大公司人才評級公司 Aspiring Minds，最近就在印度與 IT 產業關連的 500 所大學以上當中的 35,000 位大學生為對象，進行程式編寫能力調查。在調查中使用了 C、C++、C#、Java、PHP、Python 等數十種語言作為測試環境進行學術測驗。當中只有 4.77% 印度大學生達到 IT 工程師最低要求，書寫論理上正確的程式碼。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/27/indiaitfail/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2Findiaitfail%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=mrgUYd5Ed7UwA6vG9LKaBfjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=feb2cb55\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/27/indiaitfail/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"f0c65a9667e999cbc67ee680eb882bc5cd592394","tid":687516,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:46:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/National-Programming-Skills-Report-Engineers-2017-Report-Brief-10-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2FNational-Programming-Skills-Report-Engineers-2017-Report-Brief-10-694x390.jpg&h=2569eb5e&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n實驗評價分為 A4、A3、A2、A1 四個等級，能夠書寫「論理正確而機能性正確的程式碼」得到 A4 評價的學生只有 2.21%，能夠書寫「機能性正確但論理上有錯誤的程式碼」得到 A3 評價的學生只有 2.56%。得到作為 IT 工程師最低限要求的 A3、A4 評級的學生只有 4.77%。全體 31.01% 寫出「論理性與機能性都不正確的程式碼」，有 64.22% 學生更寫出「完全不能被編譯的程式碼」。<br />\n<br />\n以性別為分類的統計中，取得 A4 評價的男生佔全體 3.16%，而女生則只佔全體 0.71%。另一方面取得 A3 評級的女性只有 1.10%。換句話說能夠符合 IT 工程師要求的女性學生只佔整體 1.81%。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/National-Programming-Skills-Report-Engineers-2017-Report-Brief-14-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2FNational-Programming-Skills-Report-Engineers-2017-Report-Brief-14-694x390.jpg&h=f158a7d9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nAspiring Minds 指出，從今次調查結果可發現，如印度希望在 IT 發展持續成長，對於培育擁有高度技術力的人才，是目前當務之急。現階段有必要在歐美等地吸收技術人才。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Aspiring Minds"},{"pid":"5462b91a1bdb87642bdf7ce11c3c5482921c2093","tid":687516,"uid":61249,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20070508014156/evchk/images/4/41/Chow_indiabanana.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic3.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20070508014156%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F41%2FChow_indiabanana.jpg&h=f1aeba2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"013d69aec027d771aefb282c9694ab0ea074ce13","tid":687516,"uid":45551,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:36:29.000Z","msg":"有冇d test paper睇"},{"pid":"3ffb2b0abf824737815973e4aebac8121931413c","tid":687516,"uid":43173,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:09:59.000Z","msg":"同印度佬交過手，10個9個都勁hea，d API 10次9次都唔啱spec<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d085b2ad7011911133ce5efb5bab5ffe63ca80","tid":687516,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"留名等題目玩吓"},{"pid":"77ed62dc9ff2036361f3135e7380cef267e8bbac","tid":687516,"uid":6